edu.ncsu.csc316.security_log.dictionary

Class HashTable<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc316.security_log.dictionary.HashTable<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - Indicates that the table can work with any object type

    public class HashTable<E>
extends java.lang.Object
    An array-based hash table implementation utilizing separate chaining and golden ratio hashing. Can achieve O(1) lookups by sacrificing on space efficiency.
    Author:
    Noah Benveniste

        Parameters:
